# Ques. 1: Fibonacci Series; Write a JavaScript program to print the Fibonacci series from 0 up to a given number n.
Solution:
function findFibonacci (n){
    let a = 0;
    let b = 1;
    console.log(a);
    console.log(b);
    for(let i = 2; i < n; i++){
        let ahead = a + b;
        console.log(ahead);
        a = b;
        b = ahead;
    }
}
findFibonacci(5)

Approach:
We know that the Fibonacci series starts with 0 and 1. Each next number is the sum of the previous two numbers. So, I used a loop to calculate and print the next values.


# Ques. 2: Find the Sum of Total Digits in a Number; Write a JavaScript program to find the sum of the digits of a given number.
Solution:
function sumOfDigits(n) {
    let sum = 0;
    while (n > 0) {
        sum += n % 10;
        n = Math.floor(n / 10);
    }
    return sum;
}
console.log(sumOfDigits(9769));

Approach:
I have extracted the last digit using % 10. Then I removed it using division by 10. Then, simply repeated it until the number becomes 0 and keep adding the digits.


